WEBVTT

00:09:27.832 --> 00:09:30.387
ambao hula matunda ya kawaida
badala ya kuyaozesha,

00:09:30.411 --> 00:09:33.044
kwa nia ya kuhujumu
kilimo cha Marekani.

00:09:33.068 --> 00:09:34.598
Kwanza, unatakiwa ujue

00:09:34.622 --> 00:09:37.394
ni jeni zipi zinaongoza
kitu gani nzi wanataka kula,

00:09:37.418 --> 00:09:39.965
ambayo tayari ni mpango mrefu sana
na mgumu.

00:09:40.489 --> 00:09:43.793
Kisha urekebishe hizo jeni
kubadilisha tabia ya nzi

00:09:43.817 --> 00:09:45.355
kuwa chochote unachotaka kiwe

00:09:45.379 --> 00:09:48.180
ambayo ni mpango mrefu zaidi
na mgumu zaidi.

00:09:48.204 --> 00:09:49.522
Na inaweza isifanye kazi,

00:09:49.546 --> 00:09:52.040
kwasababu jeni
zinazoongoza tabia ni changamani


00:09:52.064 --> 00:09:54.072
Kama wewe ni gaidi
na unatakiwa uchague

00:09:54.096 --> 00:09:56.454
kati ya kuanza
programu ya utafiti yenye kuchosha


00:09:56.478 --> 00:10:00.005
itakayohitaji miaka mingi maabara
na bado isitokee vizuri,